                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-263-off1543 t18320405-263-cd1544"></join>, 12 ozs. of soap, value 6d.; 2 knives, value 2s.; 1 fork, value 1s., and 1 3/4 lb. of tea, value 10s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320405-263-victim2234" type="victimName">
